{"tid":2438280,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高院原定周四及周六審理保釋覆核 今決定增下周一聆訊","createTime":"2021-03-08T11:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T15:13:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f47c6f2310c2820e4d3486dd7eacccf016ab6308","tid":2438280,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"47人因參與民主派初選而被控串謀顛覆國家政權案，總裁判官蘇惠德上周批准其中15人保釋，律政司迅即追殺其中11人，要求覆核保釋決定，令11人須繼續還柙。高等法院法官杜麗冰上周六開庭作出指示，表示會分兩天處理11名被告的覆核，安排本周四(11日)及本周六(13日)聽取陳詞，並透露將逐個逐個即日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構最新資料顯示，高院增加下周一審理覆核申請，變成總共三天處理案件，換言之部份被告需延遲兩天始知悉最終是否獲得保釋。聆訊排期如下，預計每人聆訊一小時：<br />\n<br />\n3月11日（周四）<br />\n9:30 黃碧雲<br />\n10:30 伍健偉<br />\n<br />\n3月13日（周六）<br />\n9:30 鄭達鴻<br />\n10:30 譚文豪<br />\n11:30 郭家麒<br />\n14:00 彭卓棋<br />\n15:00 柯耀林<br />\n<br />\n3月15日（下周一）<br />\n9:30 張可森<br />\n10:30 何啟明<br />\n11:30 施德來<br />\n14:00 李予信<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/ZTBS3YSRQBA2VERXZHWTUSAM3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FZTBS3YSRQBA2VERXZHWTUSAM3U%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=eb9a1f1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FZTBS3YSRQBA2VERXZHWTUSAM3U%2F&h=67cb1d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/ZTBS3YSRQBA2VERXZHWTUSAM3U/</a>"},{"pid":"39fe7882760a84629d8b5e102ed8cba05af4ed3c","tid":2438280,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cb256cf641682ca2148ec8d6bdac8d8e271ee7","tid":2438280,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img